		<p>How can you tell when a person is too high on pain pills, zanax, valium, or any of the hundreds of &#8220;legal&#8221; drugs that are constantly pimped to the masses!<br />
 So what makes MMJ any different?  I can tell you the difference&#8230;it isn&#8217;t &#8220;physically&#8221; addictive (anything can be mental&#8230;look at food); therefore, there isn&#8217;t any money in it for the big pharmaceutical companies!  The ability or inability to test for recent use is a pathetic excuse for prohibition&#8230;why don&#8217;t we allow people to choose if they want harmful chemicals in thier bodies or not&#8230;why is it that pharmaceutical drugs meant to cure diseases or ailments cause their own disease&#8230;addiction!</p>
		
		
